{"word":"κρύβδα","slug":"κρύβδα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κρύβδα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κρύπτω'><el>κρύπτω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>without the knowledge of</i>, <el>κρύβδα Διός</el>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>clam Jove</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, like <el>κρύβδην</el>, <i>secretly</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}